dct_title_s: Map of Minnesota : school and other state lands, for sale in 1919
dct_description_sm: Tracts for sale in 1919, shown in red.; Shows state lands for sale in Koochiching, Beltrami, Cass, Itasca, St. Louis, Aitkin, Hubbard, Wadena, Carlton and Roseau counties.
